{"tid":2360742,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【破產邊緣】黃馮律師行被接管，有買樓人士資產被凍結促政府介入","createTime":"2021-01-10T05:03:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-10T15:54:07.000Z","uid":79563,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"32d8d393b64e5e1c721201ae3bad0772ae9251d6","tid":2360742,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T05:03:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1569623-20210110.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1569623-20210110.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=3UqZ%2FPYEUq8PtOmaimGdDbnp9gp%2BSvHPFRLSSJzTNPo%3D&h=e8637f28\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1569623-20210110.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=e219d097\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1569623-20210110.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n黃馮律師行早前因有前文員涉嫌不誠實挪用客戶款項，被香港律師會行使法定權力接管。一批透過該律師行進行物業買賣的苦主表示，合共有超過一億元資產被凍結，部分人未能完成物業買賣，要四出借貸還款。<br />\n<br />\n他們批評香港律師會接管黃馮律師行的做法無理，要求政府介入事件，協助苦主盡快取回資產。"},{"pid":"cbab7014f71d2064622e873a6e10ae045cd6d5d1","tid":2360742,"uid":8410,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T05:06:00.000Z","msg":"林鄭： 無所謂啦， 市場多啲銀主盤對經濟有利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad14d300b859e6bc20691d21d3be5cf317a4e707","tid":2360742,"uid":267494,"like":7,"dislike":6,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T05:07:52.000Z","msg":"呢個時候有首期仲買樓<br />\n黃極有限<br />\n律師會出名親建制<br />\n體驗下社會主義鐵拳割韭菜啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"210ab6c6537c8f641f9386188ad38fce18aa2c43","tid":2360742,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T05:08:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hk